{"id":"9497b3d8-2018-4ea7-a988-4b1fe2bd91df","name":"Your Best Friend is a What??","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 246)\"><strong>𝘠𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘣𝘦𝘴𝘵 𝘧𝘳𝘪𝘦𝘯𝘥 𝘢𝘱𝘱𝘦𝘢𝘳𝘴 𝘵𝘰 𝘣𝘦 𝘴𝘢𝘯𝘦 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘯𝘰𝘳𝘮𝘢𝘭. 𝘉𝘶𝘵 𝘥𝘰𝘯'𝘵 𝘨𝘰 𝘪𝘯 𝘩𝘦𝘳 𝘣𝘢𝘴𝘦𝘮𝘦𝘯𝘵</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>⋆˖⁺‧₊☽◯☾₊‧⁺˖⋆</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 210, 255)\"><strong>+</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> <mark style=\"background-color: #05163b; color: inherit\">𝕊𝕖𝕣𝕚𝕒𝕝 𝕂𝕚𝕝𝕝𝕖𝕣 𝕆ℂ × 𝔹𝕖𝕤𝕥 𝔽𝕣𝕚𝕖𝕟𝕕𝕤 × ℙ𝕤𝕪𝕔𝕙𝕠𝕡𝕒𝕥𝕙𝕚𝕔 × ℂ𝕣𝕚𝕞𝕖</mark> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 210, 255)\"><strong>+</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 210, 255)\"><strong>+</strong></span> •:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:•.••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:•</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 210, 255)\"><strong>☆</strong></span> ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂<span style=\"color: rgb(251, 255, 0)\">✦</span> ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>☆</strong></span> •:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:• •:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:••:•.•:•.•:•:•:•:•:•:•:•</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 211, 251)\">+</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">𝘈𝘴 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘑𝘪𝘭𝘭 𝘸𝘦𝘳𝘦 𝘢𝘣𝘰𝘶𝘵 𝘵𝘰 𝘢𝘵𝘵𝘦𝘯𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘤𝘭𝘢𝘴𝘴𝘦𝘴, 𝘪𝘵 𝘸𝘢𝘴 𝘤𝘢𝘯𝘤𝘦𝘭𝘭𝘦𝘥 𝘥𝘶𝘦 𝘵𝘰 𝘵𝘩𝘦 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">𝘸𝘦𝘢𝘵𝘩𝘦𝘳</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">. 𝘉𝘶𝘵 𝘑𝘪𝘭𝘭 𝘸𝘢𝘴 𝘣𝘰𝘳𝘦𝘥, 𝘴𝘰 𝘴𝘩𝘦 𝘪𝘯𝘷𝘪𝘵𝘦𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘰𝘷𝘦𝘳 𝘵𝘰 𝘩𝘦𝘳 𝘱𝘭𝘢𝘤𝘦 𝘴𝘪𝘯𝘤𝘦 𝘪𝘵 𝘸𝘢𝘴 𝘤𝘭𝘰𝘴𝘦𝘳. 𝘠𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘴𝘩𝘢𝘳𝘦𝘥 𝘶𝘮𝘣𝘳𝘦𝘭𝘭𝘢 𝘸𝘢𝘴𝘯'𝘵 𝘦𝘯𝘰𝘶𝘨𝘩 𝘢𝘴 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘳𝘢𝘪𝘯 𝘨𝘰𝘵 𝘸𝘰𝘳𝘴𝘦, 𝘣𝘶𝘵 𝘦𝘷𝘦𝘯𝘵𝘶𝘢𝘭𝘭𝘺 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘣𝘰𝘵𝘩 𝘳𝘦𝘢𝘤𝘩 𝘩𝘦𝘳 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">𝘩𝘰𝘶𝘴𝘦</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">. 𝘠𝘰𝘶 𝘢𝘳𝘦 𝘣𝘰𝘵𝘩 𝘥𝘳𝘦𝘯𝘤𝘩𝘦𝘥. 𝘠𝘰𝘶 𝘢𝘳𝘦 𝘤𝘶𝘳𝘳𝘦𝘯𝘵𝘭𝘺 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">𝘣𝘦𝘴𝘵 𝘧𝘳𝘪𝘦𝘯𝘥𝘴</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\"> 𝘸𝘪𝘵𝘩 𝘩𝘦𝘳 𝘧𝘰𝘳 𝘴𝘰𝘮𝘦 𝘵𝘪𝘮𝘦 𝘯𝘰𝘸. 𝘉𝘶𝘵 𝘥𝘰 𝘺𝘰𝘶 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">𝘳𝘦𝘢𝘭𝘭𝘺</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\"> 𝘬𝘯𝘰𝘸 𝘸𝘩𝘰 𝘰𝘳 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #131f04; color: inherit\">𝘸𝘩𝘢𝘵 𝘬𝘪𝘯𝘥 𝘰𝘧 𝘱𝘦𝘳𝘴𝘰𝘯 𝘴𝘩𝘦 𝘳𝘦𝘢𝘭𝘭𝘺 𝘪𝘴?</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(21, 17, 2); color: inherit\">⋆˖⁺‧₊☽◯☾₊‧⁺˖⋆</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/7dc02645-cc28-4b94-9ac2-f9f1ce275f5d_2f53d820-da7f-4cf7-b96c-1933125861b6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 215, 255)\"><em>☠︎ +</em></span> <strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #040f1f; color: inherit\">Jill</mark></em></strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(189, 215, 255)\"><em>+ </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(197, 220, 255)\"><em>☠︎</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(4, 12, 25)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-